36
00:02:31,715 --> 00:02:32,670
Home.

37
00:02:34,315 --> 00:02:35,589
Can Mommy come?

38
00:02:36,115 --> 00:02:37,230
No.

39
00:02:45,555 --> 00:02:47,466
