Yes.

55
00:03:59,235 --> 00:04:00,668
It was a good day.

56
00:04:01,235 --> 00:04:03,351
Do you ever wonder
what that would be like?

57
00:04:03,915 --> 00:04:04,825
Touch?

58
00:04:05,795 --> 00:04:06,750
No.

59
