Yes, you do.

60
00:04:11,195 --> 00:04:12,913
Occasionally. Yes.

61
00:04:14,435 --> 00:04:15,868
Touch.

62
00:04:33,395 --> 00:04:36,148
I'm not asking for it every night.
Just twice a week.

63
00:04:36,395 --> 00:04:38,989
Blue eyes.
He's never going to leave her.

64
00:04:39,235 --> 00:04:42,830
20 minutes. 20 minutes. Everything
in this damn city is 20 minutes.

65
00:04:43,075 --> 00:04:44,588
It's never 20 minutes.

66
