83
00:06:20,155 --> 00:06:24,114
She said, "What good would wings be
if you couldn't feel wind on your face?"

84
00:06:49,075 --> 00:06:52,226
On the 101 through
downtown L.A., no delays....

85
00:06:53,595 --> 00:06:55,153
Shit! Jesus!

86
00:08:01,435 --> 00:08:02,504
