94
00:08:32,595 --> 00:08:34,711
He's pretty out of it.

95
00:08:37,235 --> 00:08:38,554
The doctor's here.

96
00:09:01,435 --> 00:09:03,346
We're just going to cool to 32 today.

97
00:09:05,235 --> 00:09:06,065
Sucker.

98
00:09:09,395 --> 00:09:10,384
Jimi.

99
00:09:25,995 --> 00:09:26,825
Vein.

100
00:09:40,955 --> 00:09:42,627
Kid started walking.

101
00:09:43,435 --> 00:09:45,471
Three unassisted steps.

102
00:09:46,035 --> 00:09:48,503
-Get it on video?
-I wasn't even there.

103
