You failed as a father already.
How does that feel?

104
00:09:56,075 --> 00:09:56,951
Retrograde on.

105
00:10:01,155 --> 00:10:03,111
Come down to half flow,
give me a little volume.

106
00:10:03,435 --> 00:10:04,993
Down to half flow,
here's your volume.

107
00:10:05,235 --> 00:10:06,588
-Ready to come off?
