108
00:10:06,915 --> 00:10:07,745
Let's come off.

109
00:10:08,115 --> 00:10:09,343
We're coming down.

110
00:10:09,595 --> 00:10:12,632
We're clamped and off bypass.

111
00:10:35,875 --> 00:10:36,830
Oh, shit.

112
00:10:38,355 --> 00:10:39,470
What are you missing?

113
00:10:39,715 --> 00:10:40,511
Sponge.

114
00:10:41,915 --> 00:10:42,904
Bummer.

115
00:10:48,795 --> 00:10:49,864
Got it!

116
00:10:55,715 --> 00:10:57,068
Thank you, everybody.

117
00:10:57,435 --> 00:10:59,153
Presbyterian's on line 2.

118
00:10:59,515 --> 00:11:00,834
His rhythm will be irritable.

119
00:11:04,475 --> 00:11:07,785
-She's getting good, huh?
-Yeah, she's getting that attitude too.

120
00:11:08,115 --> 00:11:09,707
Getting an attitude?

121
00:11:12,035 --> 00:11:13,354
Shit! V-tac!

122
00:11:13,715 --> 00:11:14,989
Christ! Paddles!

123
00:11:15,395 --> 00:11:17,147
Kill the music. Get her back.

124
00:11:17,395 --> 00:11:19,386
-Charge to 2.
-Charging 200.

125
00:11:20,875 --> 00:11:21,751
Dr. Rice.

126
00:11:28,395 --> 00:11:29,271
Clear!

127
00:11:30,235 --> 00:11:31,827
